### ============================================================
### 출석 시스템 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 출석 체크인
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/attendance/check-in
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 오늘 출석 여부 확인
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/attendance/today
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 월간 출석 현황 조회 (현재 월)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/attendance/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 월간 출석 현황 조회 (특정 월)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/attendance/monthly?yearMonth=2025-01
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 현재 연속 출석 일수 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/attendance/streak
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 출석 보상 설정 초기화 (관리자용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/attendance/init
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
